import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' function OptionComponent(props) { return (
{props.title}
{props.option1}{" "} {props.option2}{" "}
) } OptionComponent.propTypes = { title:PropTypes.string, option1:PropTypes.string, option2:PropTypes.string, func:PropTypes.func, } export default OptionComponent
